TMC Handbook - Location Table Exchange Format
RASANT (Radio Aided Satellite Navigation Technique)
  derived from RTCM (Radio Technical Commission for Maritime Services) SC-104
  Keywords: RTCM -AdV, SAPOS EPS, ETRS89
  The decoding is based on the assumptions on the following homepage:
  http://www.qsl.net/dk7in/RASANT.html

